name: MauriShop
product_desc:
Our products are all pysical , they help our costumers in simplifying their life . 
We don't create the products itself we just buy it from suppliers in China basically & resell it .

Our products are in different categories : cars - cars accessories - electronics ..

We basically analyze the product before considering buying it from our suppliers , we focus on bring products that aren't available in the market and will fix huge issues for our costumers .

We just work to make life much easier for Mauritanians
high_concept: We are selling products that are hot & on demand with an affordable prices .
